{"tid":1755031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報總編輯勸澳洲政府不要相信王力強","createTime":"2019-11-25T12:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:27:42.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b014824564b17c16b962b340ebb3b4b12642c20e","tid":1755031,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"環球時報總編輯胡錫進在推特上發佈了影片︰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1198635826613080065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1198635826613080065&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4d90c3c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1198635826613080065&h=8d322c33\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1198635826613080065</a><br />\n<br />\n其中提出了關於「王力強」這個人的諸多疑點，<br />\n並表示他是一個僅僅26歲的騙子，雖然澳洲電視<br />\n節目 60 Minutes 上，這個人能明確指出間諜行<br />\n動的各項細節和人名。<br />\n <br />\n而「王力強」已證實只是採訪中所使用的化名，<br />\n但中國政府仍認真的對這個化名起了許多調查，<br />\n並且找到了「王力強」被判刑的紀錄。<br />\n <br />\n環球時報 是 人民日報社 旗下的國際新聞報紙<br />\n而 人民日報社 的所有者是 中國共產黨中央委員會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2956200c5c2d5ac671f6fa7bd84a12c74c05ae7d","tid":1755031,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUTtZcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhUTtZcH.jpg&h=beb9931f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向心龔青喺台灣被拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed058f8edcd6713ab47ffd201b9e58c59795d68a","tid":1755031,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXT2jeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXT2jeW.jpg&h=9df487a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euvW78j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuvW78j.jpg&h=3e043140&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4feb76259a7e814590545e8cf2c9c778ff17909e","tid":1755031,"uid":269864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"哦，咁即係王力強係講緊真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"}]}